snippet.title: Checkmate Showdown | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Back NOW on Kickstarter to secure Closed Beta Access: https://tinyurl.com/3mrsu9bs

Chess meets fighting games in Checkmate Showdown, an online multiplayer competitive game mixing the strategic elegance of Chess with the fast-paced execution of fighting games!
